location.fullValue: Kaufman Plan, Aldervista at North Ranch

data.description: This stunning home has the opportunity of turning the downstairs extra living space into the 5th bedroom, and the closet is already in place. The downstairs has been fully remodeled, including a full bathroom. Welcoming you is an open-concept floor plan and an open staircase.Enjoy a kitchen with upgraded quartz countertops, a backsplash, and stainless steel appliances, as well as tile flooring throughout the downstairs. The primary bedroom has one of the largest closets you will findThe second bedroom located upstairs is one of the largest rooms, measuring 15X15, and it features two walk-in closets. It can also be used as a loft. The backyard is low maintenance with beautiful upgraded rock planters all across the backyard. The backyard gazebo will be staying, and there are no neighbors behind the home. Across the street, there's a small park and plenty of parking space.
